    <string name="instruction_title">Wi-Fi ADB Setup</string>
    <string name="instruction_text">1. Open system settings (button below)\n2. Enable developer settings if not enabled:\n   - Scroll to the bottom in settings window\n   - "About headset"\n   - Scroll to the bottom\n   - Tap 7 times on "Build number"\n3. Go back (←) → open System → Developer\n4. Scroll down to "Wi-Fi debugging" section → enable\n5. Open "Wi-Fi debugging" section (tap on it)\n6. Scroll down and tap "Connect device with pairing code"\n7. Enter code in "Pairing Code" field below\n8. Press "Connect" button</string>
